{"tid":277194,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[冇朋友]星期日約左個絲打","createTime":"2017-06-09T11:40:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-09T12:18:36.000Z","uid":77724,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"503fdb1a1eedad55a1c258db3d28da8aa4ad64f4","tid":277194,"uid":77724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T11:40:33.000Z","msg":"我除左有一個拍左好耐拖嘅男友之外，<br />\n我一個真人朋友都冇，平時都係自己一個，<br />\n完全唔知啲女仔平時會做咩，<br />\n同佢見過兩次面，兩次都係去唱K,<br />\n今次都唔例外，對上一次見唔記得係半年定一年前，<br />\n可能會去睇戲，但仲未揀睇邊套，<br />\n問題在於唱K 睇戲之後仲有咩做？<br />\n<br />\n以前同同性朋友1on1相處好容易會冷場冇野講，<br />\n次次見完面都鬆一口氣，<br />\n唯獨是同呢位絲打好似冇咩呢個問題，相處都算輕鬆，<br />\n所以好想同呢位絲打做到隨時可以搵對方傾訴嘅朋友，<br />\n有冇巴打或絲打可以教我點做？"},{"pid":"358535bdf15af50fbfe44f2116d75d65d390b93c","tid":277194,"uid":16880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T11:42:51.000Z","msg":"你有無咩想買想睇呀？叫佢幫下眼囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cb82ee5c15442f483cee9d32c91002fa597ef3d","tid":277194,"uid":121922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T11:43:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d2a5e6077d797663dd8d85c03bd643e13ffe5175","tid":277194,"uid":2419,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T11:45:55.000Z","msg":"磨豆腐"},{"pid":"74058347a78b1eafa0389925f43e783afa9d742a","tid":277194,"uid":8028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T11:50:17.000Z","msg":"比埋我去好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbde0c4fe419158bd78ba02fe121018b2b5e8a54","tid":277194,"uid":52679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T11:50:54.000Z","msg":"bi ?"},{"pid":"e6dc41ecf7699172806d2b65dfc738e5c836a84d","tid":277194,"uid":77724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T11:52:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你有無咩想買想睇呀？叫佢幫下眼囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n暫時冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" 